420
00:22:19,507 --> 00:22:23,094
CERVEJA GELADA

421
00:22:29,200 --> 00:22:32,811
"Campeonato Zeta Beta Theta
Briga de Cão 2015."

422
00:22:32,812 --> 00:22:34,487
"Chad Wolcoff."

423
00:22:35,212 --> 00:22:39,648
